  "$comment": "Complete, explicit mapping from the purchased BulletPack folder onto the engine's native strip surfaces. Every path is relative to argv[2] (default ~/Downloads/BulletPack). No bullet mapping may crop a logical cell: every enemy/player source row declares its full equal-width frame count, every multi-frame row loops, and the importer proves divisibility plus non-empty alpha per frame. The importer emits seven runtime sheets (bullets, explosions, lasers, missiles, pickups, player ship and player effects); all 117 PNG files have manifest consumers and none remain staged.",
